26quot%3Bdeplores%20expressions%20of%20hatred%20directed%20against%20any%20individual%20or%20group%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshoka%20University's%20Guidelines%20on%20Protecting%20Freedom%20of%20Expression%20have%20clearly%20laid%20down%20that%20such%20freedom%20of%20expression%20is%20not%20unlimited%20and%20enjoins%20respect%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20sensibilities%20of%20others.%20This%20is%20essential%20to%20preserving%20the%20spirit%20of%20community%20at%20Ashoka.%20Actions%20that%20make%20the%20atmosphere%20intimidating%2C%20threatening%20or%20hostile%20to%20individuals%20or%20groups%20are%20therefore%20regarded%20as%20serious%20offences%20and%20are%20subject%20to%20University%20disciplinary%20procedure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711592400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fohidr6n8_ashoka-university_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcasteist-slogans-at-ashoka-university-sparks-row-5324656%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Casteist%20slogans%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20the%20students%20of%20Haryana's%20Ashoka%20University%20at%20the%20campus%2C%20sparking%20a%20flood%20of%20questions%20and%20criticism%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcasteist-slogans-at-ashoka-university-sparks-row-5324656%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcasteist-slogans-at-ashoka-university-sparks-row-5324656%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcasteist-slogans-at-ashoka-university-sparks-row-5324656%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Speaks%20Again%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Mentions%20Frozen%20Congress%20Accounts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-summons-us-diplomat-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5319322%5C%22%3Esummoned%20an%20American%20diplomat%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20their%20remarks%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DArvind-Kejriwal%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-scam%5C%22%3Eliquor%20policy%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20reiterated%20on%20Wednesday%20its%20call%20for%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20transparent%2C%20timely%20legal%20processes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20continue%20to%20follow%20these%20actions%20closely%2C%20including%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20said%20US%20State%20Department%20Spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20while%20responding%20to%20questions%20on%20India%20summoning%20Gloria%20Berbena%2C%20the%20US%20Acting%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Mission%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20at%20the%20foreign%20ministry's%20South%20Block%20office%20lasted%20nearly%2040%20minutes%20yesterday%20with%20India%20objecting%20strongly%20to%20the%20US%20remarks%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiller%20also%20responded%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Congress%20party's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-dont-have-money-to-spend-congress-chief-weeks-before-lok-sabha-polls-5233411%5C%22%3Efrozen%20bank%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20the%20Congress%20party's%20allegations%20that%20tax%20authorities%20have%20frozen%20some%20of%20their%20bank%20accounts%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20will%20make%20it%20challenging%20to%20effectively%20campaign%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-summons-us-diplomat-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5319322%5C%22%3EIndia%20Summons%20US%20Diplomat%20Over%20Comments%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20US%20encourages%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20transparent%20and%20timely%20legal%20processes%26quot%3B%20for%20each%20of%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20respect%20to%20your%20first%20question%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20any%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20what%20we%20have%20said%20publicly%20is%20what%20I%20just%20said%20from%20here%2C%20that%20we%20encourage%20fair%2C%20transparent%2C%20timely%20legal%20processes.%20We%20don't%20think%20anyone%20should%20object%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20last%20week%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20the%20third%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20after%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fencourage-fair-transparent-legal-process-us-on-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-5313351%5C%22%3Emonitoring%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20and%20called%20on%20New%20Delhi%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Ba%20fair%20and%20timely%20legal%20process%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20jailed%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20objected%20to%20it%20and%20warned%20of%20%26quot%3Bunhealthy%20precedents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fencourage-fair-transparent-legal-process-us-on-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-5313351%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEncourage%20Fair%2C%20Transparent%20Legal%20Process%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStates%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20respectful%20of%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20internal%20affairs%20of%20others%2C%20and%20this%20responsibility%20is%20even%20more%20so%20in%20case%20of%20fellow%20democracies.%20It%20could%20otherwise%20end%20up%20setting%20unhealthy%20precedents%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20legal%20processes%20are%20based%20on%20an%20independent%20judiciary%20which%20is%20committed%20to%20objective%20and%20timely%20outcomes.%20Casting%20aspersions%20on%20that%20is%20unwarranted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20remarks%20came%20days%20after%20Germany's%20Foreign%20Office%20stressed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20trial.%20The%20Indian%20government%20had%20reacted%20strongly%20and%20summoned%20the%20German%20envoy%2C%20labelling%20their%20remark%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20interference%20in%20internal%20matters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20excise%20policy%20was%20introduced%20to%20bring%20an%20overhaul%20to%20the%20liquor%20business%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20was%20scrapped%20after%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20policy.%20The%20ED%20believes%20the%20bribe%20money%20from%20the%20policy%20was%20allegedly%20used%20for%20funding%20the%20AAP's%20election%20campaigns.%20It%20has%20also%20called%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspirator%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20arrest%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20has%20also%20prompted%20furious%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711591020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F17vl2e2c_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-speaks-again-on-arvind-kejriwal-mentions-frozen-congress-accounts-5324508%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20India%20summoned%20an%20American%20diplomat%20over%20their%20remarks%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20the%20US%20reiterated%20on%20Wednesday%20its%20call%20for%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20transparent%2C%20timely%20legal%20processes%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-speaks-again-on-arvind-kejriwal-mentions-frozen-congress-accounts-5324508%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbsurd%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20Bureaucrats%20Slam%20Economist%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal's%20UPSC%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20bureaucrats%20on%20Wednesday%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bavoidable%26quot%3B%20the%20comments%20of%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20member%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20that%20five%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20by%20lakhs%20of%20students%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwaste%20of%20youthful%20energy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20millions%20aspire%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20sought-after%20government%20services%20to%20contribute%20towards%20nation-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanyal%20has%20said%20that%20one%20should%20only%20attempt%20UPSC%20or%20other%20such%20examinations%20if%20one%20wants%20to%20become%20an%20administrator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20mentioned%2C%20it%20(is)%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20attempt%20the%20UPSC%20or%20other%20such%20exams%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20person%20wants%20to%20be%20an%20administrator.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20lakhs%20of%20people%20are%20spending%205-8%20years%20repeatedly%20doing%20this%20exam%20as%20a%20'way%20of%20life'.%20This%20is%20such%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20comments%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20G%20Sundaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20absurd.%20India%20is%20a%20vast%20country.%20We%20are%20interested%20in%20a%20united%20India%20and%20that%20is%20why%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20(the%20first%20home%20minister%20of%20Independent%20India)%20created%20these%20services%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%2C%20among%20others.%20It%20is%20all%20working%20well.%26quot%3B%20There%20may%20be%20certain%20deficiencies%20which%20can%20of%20course%20be%20rectified%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESundaram%2C%20a%201962-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Gujarat%20cadre%2C%20who%20superannuated%20as%20the%20Tourism%20Secretary%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20(Sanyal's)%20comments%20were%20completely%20avoidable.%26quot%3B%20The%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20conducts%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20every%20year%20in%20three%20stages%20--%20preliminary%2C%20main%20and%20personality%20test%20(interview)%20--%20to%20select%20officers%20for%20different%20central%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20K%20Sarkar%2C%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%2C%20said%20Sanyal's%20assertion%20was%20avoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%20or%20resources.%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20his%20assertion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%201979-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20West%20Bengal%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20aspire%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20government%20services.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20best%20services%20in%20India%20to%20contribute%20towards%20nation-building%20and%20development.%20His%20comments%20were%20avoidable.%26quot%3B%20Former%20IAS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chopra%20said%20Sanyal%20is%20entitled%20to%20his%20views%20but%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20youths%20who%20wish%20to%20be%20civil%20servants%20is%20not%20in%20good%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20aspires%20to%20be%20an%20Ambani.%20People%20also%20want%20to%20be%20poets%2C%20painters%20and%20thespians.%20Many%20want%20to%20work%20for%20the%20government.%20And%20in%20the%20government%20there%20is%20no%20job%20more%20fulfilling%20than%20a%20district%20assignment%2C%20or%20a%20posting%20as%20a%20JS%20(joint%20secretary)%20in%20which%20you%20cover%20the%20entire%20domain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanyal%20is%20of%20course%20entitled%20to%20his%20views%2C%20but%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20young%20women%20and%20men%20who%20wish%20to%20be%20civil%20servants%20is%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra%2C%20a%201985-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20Director%20of%20Mussoorie-based%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20of%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20--%20the%20country's%20premier%20training%20institute%20for%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20bureaucrat%2C%20Kiran%20Puri%2C%20said%20preparing%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20waste%20of%20youthful%20energy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20academically%20strong%20and%20knowledgeable%2C%20they%20only%20join%20the%20civil%20services.%20Civil%20servants%20are%20needed%20to%20run%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%201983-batch%20Central%20Secretariat%20Service%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20talented%20people%20do%20not%20devote%20their%20energy%20and%20attention%20towards%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20then%20how%20will%20the%20nation's%20development%20be%20ensured%2C%20she%20posed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20the%20best%20of%20minds%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20country%20and%20to%20ensure%20further%20ease%20of%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Puri%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Joint%20Secretary%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Administrative%20Reforms%20and%20Public%20Grievances%20under%20the%20Union%20Personnel%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20S%20Y%20Quraishi%2C%20however%2C%20partially%20agreed%20with%20Sanyal's%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20partially%20right.%20Young%20people%20are%20putting%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%20preparing%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%20Some%20people%20leave%20lucrative%20jobs%20and%20hefty%20salaries%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20these%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20suggested%20limiting%20the%20number%20of%20attempts%20being%20provided%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20too%20many%20attempts%20being%20provided%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%20It%20can%20be%20limited%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20attempts%20as%20it%20was%20earlier.%20There%20may%20be%20some%20extra%20attempts%20for%20people%20belonging%20to%20scheduled%20caste%2C%20scheduled%20tribe%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServing%20IPS%20officer%20Pankaj%20Chaudhary%20also%20disagreed%20with%20Sanyal's%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCivil%20services%20exam%20and%20the%20UPSC%20act%20as%20the%20role%20model%20for%20many%20youngsters.%20These%20comments%20were%20completely%20avoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%202009-batch%20IPS%20officer%20of%20Rajasthan%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20civil%20services%20examination%20is%20transparent%20and%20provides%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20topper%20of%20Hindi%20in%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%20in%202008.%20A%20person%20like%20me%20from%20a%20Hindi%20background%20could%20become%20a%20part%20of%20this%20service%20as%20the%20UPSC%20and%20civil%20services%20examination%20shows%20it%20is%20very%20credible%20and%20unbiased%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20is%20Superintendent%20of%20Community%20Policing%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711590720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F90g08j8g_sanjeev-sanyal-principal-econnomic-advisor-650_625x300_04_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabsurd-ex-bureaucrats-slam-economist-sanjeev-sanyals-upsc-remark-5322980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20bureaucrats%20on%20Wednesday%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bavoidable%26quot%3B%20the%20comments%20of%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20member%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20that%20five%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20by%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabsurd-ex-bureaucrats-slam-economist-sanjeev-sanyals-upsc-remark-5322980%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Divers%20Find%202%20Bodies%20In%20Submerged%20Truck%20After%20Bridge%20Collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20two%20construction%20workers%20were%20found%20in%20the%20cold%20waters%20of%20Baltimore%20harbor%20Wednesday%2C%20trapped%20in%20their%20red%20pick-up%20truck%20after%20a%20giant%20cargo%20ship%20slammed%20into%20the%20bridge%20they%20had%20been%20filling%20potholes%20on%2C%20causing%20a%20thunderous%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryland%20police%20announced%20the%20grim%20discovery%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20adding%20that%20sonar%20shows%20what%20they%20believe%20are%20more%20vehicles%20trapped%20within%20the%20concrete%20and%20twisted%20steel%20debris%20of%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20of%20the%20eight-man%20construction%20crew%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20with%20four%20bodies%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarning%20that%20it%20was%20not%20safe%20for%20divers%20to%20try%20to%20penetrate%20the%20wreckage%2C%20police%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20they%20were%20shifting%20to%20a%20salvage%20operation%2C%20removing%20the%20superstructure%20and%20then%20sending%20divers%20back%20in%20to%20recover%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20sonar%20scans%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20that%20the%20vehicles%20are%20encased%20in%20the%20superstructure%20and%20concrete%20that%20we%20tragically%20saw%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Colonel%20Roland%20Butler%2C%20the%20superintendent%20of%20Maryland's%20state%20police%2C%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20container%20ship%20Dali%2C%20about%201%2C000%20feet%20(300%20meters)%20long%2C%20and%20piled%20high%20with%20cargo%2C%20was%20leaving%20the%20busy%20port%20at%201%3A30%20am%20Tuesday%20en%20route%20to%20Asia%20when%20power%20failed%20and%20the%20vessel%20crashed%20straight%20into%20a%20support%20column.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20the%20entire%20steel%20structure%20--%20crossed%20by%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20motorists%20each%20day%20--%20collapsed%20within%20seconds%2C%20cascading%20over%20the%20bow%20of%20the%20ship%2C%20blocking%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20US%20trading%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20issued%20a%20Mayday%20call%20in%20the%20moments%20before%20the%20collision%2C%20prompting%20police%20to%20rush%20to%20stop%20traffic%20on%20the%20bridge%20--%20likely%20saving%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20no%20chance%20to%20evacuate%20the%20eight%20workers%20filling%20potholes%20on%20the%20road%20directly%20above%20the%20oncoming%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EButler%20named%20the%20two%20victims%20found%20Wednesday%20as%20Alejandro%20Hernandez%20Fuentes%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20who%20had%20lived%20in%20Baltimore%20but%20was%20originally%20from%20Mexico%2C%20and%20his%2026-year-old%20colleague%20Dorlian%20Ronial%20Castillo%20Cabrera%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20suburb%20of%20Dundalk%20but%20came%20from%20Guatemala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20found%20in%2025%20feet%20of%20water%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20others%20were%20pulled%20from%20the%20water%20alive%20in%20the%20moments%20after%20the%20collapse%20early%20Tuesday.%20One%20was%20uninjured%2C%20while%20the%20second%20was%20released%20from%20hospital%20Wednesday%2C%20Butler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20more%20workers%20are%20presumed%20dead%2C%20vanished%20into%20the%20swirling%20currents%20and%20crumpled%20tangle%20of%20wrecked%20girders%20and%20pylons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Hard-working'%20men%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%2C%20which%20remained%20entangled%20in%20the%20debris%20Wednesday%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bstable%2C%26quot%3B%20Coast%20Guard%20Vice%20Admiral%20Peter%20Gautier%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20mostly%20Indian%20crew%20remained%20on%20board%20and%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20much%20engaged%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%2C%20a%20federal%20authority%2C%20said%20that%20the%20ship's%20data%20record%2C%20or%20black%20box%2C%20had%20been%20recovered%20so%20that%20investigators%20can%20understand%20what%20went%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautier%20insisted%20the%20ship%20did%20not%20present%20an%20environmental%20danger%2C%20despite%20the%20billion%20and%20a%20half%20gallons%20of%20oil%20and%20few%20dozen%20hazardous%20material%20cargo%20containers%20on%20board.%20Two%20other%20containers%20--%20of%20the%20total%204%2C700