0arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Washington%20on%20Wednesday%20stressed%20that%20it%20encourages%20fair%2C%20transparent%20and%20timely%20legal%20processes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-arvind-kejriwal-remarks-us-speaks-on-congress-frozen-accounts-5323334%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turtles%2C%20Mice%2C%20Scorpions%20May%20Become%20More%20Common%20In%20Major%20US%20Cities%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPeregrine%20falcons%20perched%20atop%20towering%20skyscrapers.%20Coyotes%20caught%20on%20camera%20playing%20in%20someone's%20backyard.%20The%20pale%20green%20wings%20of%20a%20cabbage%20white%20butterfly%20perched%20on%20a%20flower%20blossom.%20Urban%20areas%20are%20awash%20in%20wildlife%20that%20faces%20growing%20pressures%20due%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20today%20in%20PLOS%20ONE.%20The%20research%2C%20which%20looked%20at%20climate%20impacts%20on%20everything%20from%20mammals%20to%20insects%20in%2060%20of%20the%20most%20populous%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20found%20that%20a%20warming%20world%20is%20moving%20many%20animals%20out%20of%20their%20historical%20geographic%20ranges%20and%20into%20new%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20a%20few%20years%2C%20the%20animals%20that%20you%20feed%20at%20your%20bird%20feeder%20might%20look%20very%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alessandro%20Filazzola%2C%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%2C%20who%20completed%20the%20research%20while%20he%20was%20a%20postdoctoral%20fellow%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%20Mississauga's%20Centre%20for%20Urban%20Environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilazzola%20and%20his%20team%20leveraged%20data%20from%20the%20Global%20Biodiversity%20Information%20Facility%2C%20which%20pulls%20data%20from%20community%20science%20apps%20like%20iNaturalist%20and%20eBird%2C%20to%20estimate%20roughly%20how%20many%20species%20are%20currently%20present%20in%20urban%20areas.%20They%20then%20paired%20that%20information%20with%20United%20Nations%20climate%20projections%20known%20as%20shared%20socioeconomic%20pathways%2C%20or%20SSPs.%20The%20researchers%20looked%20at%20what%20happened%20to%20wildlife%20under%20three%20different%20scenarios%2C%20from%20moderate%20warming%20of%201.4C%20over%20pre-industrial%20levels%20by%202100%20-%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Agreement%20-%20to%20a%20mid-range%20warming%20of%203.6C%20to%20the%20most%20extreme%20possible%20warming%20of%204.4C%20with%20continued%20development%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20So%20far%20the%20planet%20has%20warmed%20by%201.3C%20over%20pre-industrial%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20cities%20are%20seeing%20large%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Filazzola.%20%26quot%3BMany%20species%20are%20moving%20in%20and%20many%20species%20are%20moving%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20broad%20trends%20identified%20in%20the%20study%3A%20Most%20vertebrates%2C%20including%20loons%2C%20canids%20(which%20includes%20coyotes)%20and%20amphibians%20will%20become%20less%20common%20across%20the%20cities%20studied.%20So%20too%20will%20the%20seemingly%20ubiquitous%20earthworm%2C%20though%20only%20one%20species%20of%20earthworm%20showed%20up%20in%20the%20data.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20turtles%2C%20scorpions%20and%20(in%20an%20exception%20to%20the%20vertebrates%20decline)%20mice%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20broadly%20expected%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fiq2tvoa8_bloomberg-species-graph_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEcologists%20are%20already%20very%20aware%20that%20species%20ranges%20are%20shifting%20with%20a%20changing%20climate%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20surprising%20that%20this%20is%20also%20happening%20to%20a%20significant%20extent%20in%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carly%20Ziter%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20biology%20at%20Concordia%20University%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20something%20that%20I've%20seen%20as%20much%20attention%20paid%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20under%20the%20lowest%20warming%20scenario%2C%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20cities%20studied%20can%20expect%20at%20least%2050%20new%20species%20to%20move%20in%20and%2040%20to%20move%20out%2C%20though%20the%20turnover%20isn't%20evenly%20distributed.%20Toronto%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20lose%20between%2040%20and%20195%20of%20its%20estimated%20888%20species%2C%20but%20could%20gain%20between%20159%20and%20360%20new%20species%20by%202100%20(where%20higher%20rates%20of%20warming%20are%20associated%20with%20both%20increased%20species%20loss%20and%20gains).%20Quebec%20City%20and%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska%20are%20also%20among%20the%20cities%20predicted%20to%20have%20the%20largest%20increase%20in%20new%20species%20while%20experiencing%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20loss.%20In%20contrast%2C%20places%20like%20Atlanta%2C%20San%20Antonio%20and%20Austin%20are%20expected%20to%20lose%20more%20species%20than%20they%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20wildlife%20in%20jeopardy%3A%20Atlanta%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20on%20track%20to%20lose%2013.5%25%20of%20tree%20species%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20century%2C%20the%20study%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cities%20with%20the%20lowest%20levels%20of%20expected%20species%20turnover%20are%20in%20the%20arid%20Southwest%20and%20include%20Las%20Vegas%20as%20well%20as%20Mesa%20and%20Tucson%20in%20Arizona.%20While%20climate%20change%20will%20likely%20make%20those%20places%20even%20drier%2C%20researchers%20suspect%20those%20ecosystems%20are%20already%20resilient%20to%20the%20encroaching%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilazzola%20cautions%20that%20his%20study%20is%20a%20model%20study%20and%2C%20as%20such%2C%20has%20limitations.%20While%20the%20researchers%20only%20looked%20at%20climate%20as%20a%20factor%2C%20other%20factors%20such%20as%20species%20interaction%20are%20not%20captured%20by%20the%20model%20and%20could%20impact%20outcomes.%20But%20he%20hopes%20that%20the%20findings%20will%20encourage%20other%20researchers%20to%20follow%20this%20line%20of%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecies%20turnover%20isn't%20just%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20climate%20impacts%2C%20Filazzola%20notes%3A%20As%20animals%20move%20from%20their%20ecological%20niche%2C%20they%20can%20create%20nuisances%20for%20humans.%20Already%2C%20Southern%20Californians%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20growing%20mosquito%20problem%20as%20Aedes%20mosquitoes%2C%20a%20species%20with%20a%20strong%20preference%20for%20biting%20humans%2C%20have%20moved%20into%20the%20region%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECities%20are%20also%20the%20site%20of%20frequent%20human-wildlife%20interactions%2C%20including%20both%20conflicts%20and%20delight.%20%26quot%3BWith%20this%20great%20urban%20shift%2C%20many%20people%20will%20need%20to%20re-learn%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20wildlife%20around%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ziter%20said.%20%26quot%3BParticular%20species%20can%20also%20have%20immense%20cultural%20or%20relational%20value%20for%20people.%20Even%20for%20urban%20dwellers%20who%20might%20see%20themselves%20as%20separate%20from%20nature%2C%20I%20think%20many%20people%20would%20feel%20less%20connected%20to%20where%20they%20live%20if%20familiar%20species%20were%20to%20disappear%20from%20the%20landscape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711589940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fgmjsoam_mouse_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fturtles-mice-scorpions-may-become-more-common-in-major-us-cities-study-5324511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20research%20looked%20at%20climate%20impacts%20on%20everything%20from%20mammals%20to%20insects%20in%2060%20of%20the%20most%20populous%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fturtles-mice-scorpions-may-become-more-common-in-major-us-cities-study-5324511%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20pours%20additional%20%242.75%20bn%20into%20Anthropic%2C%20total%20investment%20at%20%244%20bn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711588813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F16%2Ffull%2F1708048506-2242.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-pours-additional-2-75-bn-into-anthropic-total-investment-at-4-bn-124032800015_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20companies%20are%20collaborating%20to%20develop%20so-called%20foundation%20models%2C%20which%20underpin%20the%20generative%20AI%20systems%20that%20have%20captured%20global%20attention%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-pours-additional-2-75-bn-into-anthropic-total-investment-at-4-bn-124032800015_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-pours-additional-2-75-bn-into-anthropic-total-investment-at-4-bn-124032800015_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-pours-additional-2-75-bn-into-anthropic-total-investment-at-4-bn-124032800015_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20vs%20Congress%20Over%20Key%20Karnataka%20Seat%2C%20Legislators%20Threaten%20To%20Quit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20point%20where%20it%20was%20reportedly%20struggling%20to%20get%20ministers%20and%20lawmakers%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20now%20found%20itself%20facing%20a%20problem%20of%20plenty%20as%20well%20as%20a%20public%20feud%20in%20the%20prestige%20constituency%20of%20Kolar.%20Five%20legislators%20from%20the%20party%2C%20including%20a%20minister%2C%20have%20threatened%20to%20resign%20over%20the%20former%20MP%20from%20the%20seat%20pushing%20for%20his%20son-in-law%20to%20be%20named%20the%20candidate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20has%20brought%20factionalism%20in%20the%20Congress%20out%20in%20the%20open%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20hoping%20to%20do%20well%20this%20time.%20In%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20had%20managed%20to%20get%20its%20candidate%20elected%20in%20just%20one%20of%20the%2028%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20had%20also%20lost%20Kolar%2C%20where%20it%20had%20won%20every%20single%20time%20-%20barring%20one%20-%20since%20the%20first%20general%20elections%20in%201952.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201991%2C%20the%20constituency%20was%20won%20by%20KH%20Muniyappa%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20minister%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20cabinet%20and%20is%20seeking%20a%20ticket%20for%20his%20son-in-law%20Chikka%20Peddanna.%20Even%20though%20the%20party%20has%20not%20announced%20the%20candidate%20yet%2C%20three%20MLAs%20from%20Kolar%20district%2C%20including%20a%20minister%2C%20and%20two%20members%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%20(MLCs)%20have%20already%20threatened%20to%20resign%20over%20the%20proposed%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objection%20stems%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20Mr%20Pedanna%20getting%20the%20ticket%20would%20ensure%20representation%20for%20communities%20classified%20as%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)-Left%20in%20Karnataka%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20SC-Right%2C%20which%20the%20legislators%20are%20pushing%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20who%20have%20threatened%20to%20resign%20are%20G%20Manjunath%20(Kolar%20Assembly%20constituency)%2C%20KY%20Nanjegowda%20(Malur%20constituency)%20and%20MC%20Sudhakar%20(Chintamani%20constituency)%20and%20the%20MLCs%20are%20Anil%20Kumar%20and%20Naseer%20Ahmed.%20Mr%20Sudhakar%20is%20the%20state's%20higher%20education%20minister%20and%20Mr%20Ahmed%20is%20the%20political%20secretary%20to%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20MLCs%20met%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20chairman%20and%20showed%20their%20resignation%20letters%20to%20journalists%2C%20the%20MLAs%20were%20planning%20to%20meet%20the%20Assembly%20Speaker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sudhakar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20all%20respect%20for%20the%20party%20high%20command%2C%20but%20here%20we%20want%20others%20to%20get%20representation.%20That%20is%20the%20only%20issue.%20Since%20some%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20high%20command%20to%20get%20the%20seat%2C%20we%20thought%20there%20is%20no%20point%20continuing.%20We%20would%20rather%20sit%20at%20home%20than%20continue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20all%20the%20legislators%20decided%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20their%20resignations%20after%20being%20asked%20to%20do%20so%20by%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Congress%20state%20chief%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar.%20Urban%20Development%20Minister%20BS%20Suresha%20rushed%20to%20meet%20the%20legislators%20to%20convince%20them%20not%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Muniyappa%2C%20who%20is%20a%20seven-time%20MP%20from%20Kolar%20and%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20S%20Muniswamy%20in%202019%2C%20said%20he%20could%20win%20the%20seat%20again%20if%20given%20the%20chance%20but%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20party%20leadership's%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20things%20happen%20but%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20it%20has%20reached%20a%20peak%20now.%20We%20had%20all%20met%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20I%20told%20them%20I%20had%20lost%20the%20elections%20only%20once%20and%20appealed%20to%20them%20to%20give%20an%20opportunity%20and%20I%20would%20win%20the%20seat.%20They%20(the%20other%20side)%20also%20proposed%20some%20names.%20All%20MLAs%20had%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20decision%20to%20the%20party%20high%20command%20and%20we%20will%20abide%20by%20it.%20That%20was%20the%20end%20and%20this%20is%20a%20surprise%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20anything%20on%20the%20issue.%20I%20am%20a%20disciplined%20soldier%20of%20the%20party%20and%20will%20abide%20by%20whatever%20the%20leadership%20decides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Constituency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%2C%20Deve%20Gowda's%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%2C%20also%20had%20disagreements%20about%20who%20would%20keep%20the%20Kolar%20constituency%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20finally%20getting%20it%20in%20its%20quota%20of%20three.%20For%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20seat%20is%20doubly%20important%20because%20the%20party%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20last%20year%20and%20has%20been%20hoping%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20the%2025%20constituencies%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20Scientist%20Professor%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20clearly%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20Congress.%20They%20lost%20the%20seat%20after%20many%20elections%20last%20time%20and%20now%2C%20in%20their%20effort%20to%20regain%20it%2C%20several%20groups%20in%20Kolar%20are%20fighting%20for%20space.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20test%20for%20its%20conflict%20management.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20the%20Congress'%20scale%20of%20victory%20in%20the%202023%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20won%20135%20of%20the%20state's%20224%20seats%2C%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20flipside%2C%20Mr%20Shastri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20about%20local%20level%20unity%20in%20the%20constituency%20-%20do%20faction%20leaders%20come%20together%20to%20get%20their%20candidate%20to%20win%20or%20do%20they%20use%20the%20opportunity%20to%20get%20their%20candidate%20to%20lose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20will%20be%20critical%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20push%20its%20message%20of%20five%20guarantees%2C%20which%20was%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20its%20Assembly%20polls%20win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711587840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fn86bq49c_congress-generic-getty_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-vs-congress-over-key-karnataka-seat-5-legislators-threaten-to-quit-5324390%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20a%20point%20where%20it%20was%20reportedly%20struggling%20to%20get%20ministers%20and%20lawmakers%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20now%20found%20itself%20facing%20a%20problem%20of%20plenty%20as%20well%20as%20a%20public%20feud%20in%20the%20prestige%20constituency%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-vs-congress-over-key-karnataka-seat-5-legislators-threaten-to-quit-5324390%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenan%20Thompson%20Says%20%E2%80%98My%20Heart%20Goes%20Out%E2%80%99%20to%20Fellow%20Nickelodeon%20Stars%20Featured%20in%20%E2%