ecials%2Fbs-events%2Fhow-bs-swam-against-the-media-tide-to-create-a-unique-identity-for-itself-124032701050_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fspecials%2Fbs-events%2Fhow-bs-swam-against-the-media-tide-to-create-a-unique-identity-for-itself-124032701050_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Welcoming%20Tainted%20Leaders%3F%20%26quot%3BDoors%20Open%20For%20All%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Finance%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAll%20major%20political%20parties%20encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20nobody%20has%20a%20moral%20authority%20to%20say%20anything%20as%20it%20was%20legal%20and%20according%20to%20law%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20given%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment%20against%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20more%20debate%20is%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20better%20system%20for%20electoral%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20law%2C%20now%20scrapped%20by%20the%20top%20court%2C%20was%20passed%20by%20parliament%20and%20the%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20as%20per%20the%20prevailing%20law%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20passed%20by%20parliament%20and%20based%20on%20the%20law%2C%20bonds%20were%20bought%20and%20encashed%20by%20all%20parties%20but%20one...%20Everyone%20has%20received%20from%20everybody.%20Every%20donor%20has%20given%20to%20everybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20party%20which%20now%20says%20this%20is%20a%20scam%2C%20this%20is%20a%20scandal%2C%20had%20also%20taken%20money%20through%20the%20bonds.%20Tell%20me%20what%20moral%20authority%20anyone%20has%20to%20speak%20because%20it%20was%20the%20law%20then...%20it%20went%20lawfully.%20It%20was%20a%20step%20better%20than%20what%20prevailed%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20the%20new%20government%20can%20do%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20she%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20better%20the%20system%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20still%20better%20than%20the%20previous%20system%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20what%20we've%20gone%20back%20to%20now.%20We%20need%20to%20do%20something%20better%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20more%20work%20is%20required%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20five-judge%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20said%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20under%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20of%20connections%20between%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20raids%20and%20bond%20purchases%2C%20stating%20that%20even%20companies%20that%20donated%20to%20the%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20raided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BED%20raids%20still%20happened.%20It%20did%20not%20give%20them%20(companies)%20any%20immunity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20added%20that%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20are%20not%20acting%20with%20any%20political%20agenda%20as%20the%20law%20pursues%20those%20who%20disobey%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStop%20making%20political%20arguments%20over%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20welcoming%20tainted%20politicians%2C%20she%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdoors%20are%20open%20for%20all%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20see%20work%20happening...%20and%20a%20party%20is%20making%20a%20difference%2C%20they%20obviously%20would%20want%20to%20come%20and%20join.%20But%20the%20BJP%20has%20value%20systems%20and%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20party%20runs%20under%20certain%20leadership.%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20ever%20a%20compromise%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20on%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate's%20remarks%20against%20BJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20she%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Babhorrent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shrinate%20should%20have%20tendered%20an%20unconditional%20apology%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20controversial%20comment%20was%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Shrinate's%20accounts%20about%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20the%20actor%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20from%20Mandi%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20row%2C%20Ms%20Shrinate%20removed%20the%20post%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20posted%20by%20her%20but%20by%20someone%20who%20had%20access%20to%20her%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20refused%20to%20call%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20a%20case%20of%20political%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20not%20complied%20with%20several%20ED%20summonses%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20governance%20has%20gone%20down%20the%20drain%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20-%20the%20two%20states%20where%20the%20AAP%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711562220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqgumto4o_nirmala-sitharaman-pti_625x300_31_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-party-has-moral-authority-to-speak-against-poll-bonds-says-nirmala-sitharaman-5321843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20major%20political%20parties%20encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20nobody%20has%20a%20moral%20authority%20to%20say%20anything%20as%20it%20was%20leg