lcy%20that%20returns%20to%20where%20we%20are%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20troop%20deployment%20will%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20relationship%20going%20forward.%20And%20we've%20been%20very%2C%20very%20honest%20with%20the%20Chinese%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20China%2C%20the%20relationship%20has%20been%20difficult%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20a%20boundary%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20despite%20the%20boundary%20dispute%20over%20the%20many%20years%2C%20we%20built%20up%20a%20substantial%20relationship%20because%20we%20agreed%20that%20while%20we%20will%20negotiate%20the%20boundary%20dispute%2C%20both%20of%20us%20will%20agree%20that%20we%20will%20not%20bring%20soldiers%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20the%20boundary.%20And%20we%20will%20never%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20there'll%20be%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20understanding%20which%20started%20in%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20actually%20was%20reflected%20in%20several%20agreements.%20And%20those%20agreements%20gave%20the%20relationship%20stability%20based%20on%20which%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20the%20relationship%20went%20forward%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20for%20reasons%20still%20not%20clear%20to%20us%2C%20these%20agreements%20were%20broken%20in%202020.%20And%20we%20had%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20China%20nose-dived%20significantly%20following%20the%20deadly%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%