20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%20They%20also%20linked%20the%20plot%20to%20murder%20Pannun%20with%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPannun%20has%20also%20been%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20home%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711551424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19184738%2FHardeep-Singh-Nijjar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fafter-ib-ministry-order-youtube-blocks-india-from-viewing-australian-show-on-nijjar-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Australian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20said%20its%20journalists%20faced%20pressure%20from%20Indian%20authorities%20while%20working%20on%20the%20story%2C%20which%20covered%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20government%20agents%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Sikh%20activist%20in%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fafter-ib-ministry-order-youtube-blocks-india-from-viewing-australian-show-on-nijjar-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UltraTech%20to%20buy%2026%25%20stake%20in%20O2%20Renewable%20for%20green%20energy%20needs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711551302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F30%2Ffull%2F1701352096-704.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fultratech-to-buy-26-stake-in-o2-renewable-for-green-energy-needs-124032701020_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cement%20maker%20company%20has%20entered%20into%20an%20energy%20supply%20agreement%20and%20share%20subscription%20and%20shareholders%20agreement%20with%20O2%20Renewable%20Energy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi